{
  "chapter": 114,
  "chapter_summary": "第114回\"邪不敌正\"：轩辕三光在赌场散场后被屠娇娇和白开心拦住，正要追赌债时，轩辕三光突然惊恐逃回——原来他在街上撞见了被燕南天押着的江别鹤。燕南天身形枯瘦但威风凛凛，将江别鹤擒住要带他去找小鱼儿亲手报仇。小仙女张菁和顾人玉路过此地，小仙女认出江别鹤上前挑衅，却被燕南天一招制服。燕南天教训二人不可恃强凌弱后，众人得知燕南天身份皆惊。江玉郎突然出现向燕南天敬酒，谎称与江小鱼是患难之交，燕南天急切想见小鱼儿，竟信了江玉郎的话，带着他匆匆离去。江别鹤虽被押着，嘴角却偷偷露出笑容，暗示江玉郎的出现可能是父子二人的阴谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "格老子，真他妈的是天光、人光、钱光，反正弄不到鸟蛋精光，老子也睡不着觉。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两个龟儿子为什么还不走，难道还想跟老子赌？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这里只有一个半龟儿子，还有半个是龟女儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这里只有一个龟儿子，我却是你祖奶奶。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，那赌鬼的轻功一向并不高明，咱们一定能追得上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你这是干什么？难道撞见了鬼么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "正是撞见了大头鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子长得倒真有些奇怪，江湖中有这么样一个怪人，我居然没听说过，也没有见过，可见我这些年来实在太懒了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "恶赌鬼，你认得这人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤怎会没有跟着魏无牙？反而跟这怪人走到一起来了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，快来呀，你骑的马难道是三条腿的么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "不是我慢，而是你骑得实在太快了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "谁敢说我马骑得太快，我撞过人么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你……你不快。是……是我太慢。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "这样才乖，姐姐请你吃宵夜。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天真可说是九丫头的好日子，我也很开心，所以我一定要大吃一顿，而且还要喝两杯。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你叹什么气？九丫头心上有了别的人，你难道很难受么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "我怎会难受，我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你不难受最好，你看，这里居然还有粉蒸肉，还有珍珠丸子，我已经有好几年没有吃过这种小吃了，因为除了湖北外，别的地方做的都不好吃。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎会到了这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，堂堂的江南大侠，怎会躲到这种小地方来了，难道是已经不敢见人了么，难怪江湖中人都说江大侠已失踪了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江别鹤，江大侠，你为什么不开口了？你以前不是能说会道的吗？而且我还记得你的威风不小。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江别鹤，你用不着装傻，装傻也没用，不知有多少人正等着找你算一算旧账，你就跟着我走吧。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "他不能跟你走！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "他为什么不能跟我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "只因他要跟我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "跟你走，你是什么东西！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你是谁家的子弟？怎的不分皂白，就敢对人下这么重的手？江湖中的后辈，怎地越来越不懂规矩了？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你才是后辈小子！你才不懂规矩，你可知道……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "我被人如此欺负，你非但不帮我的忙，还不准我说话，你还能算是男人么？难怪别人要叫你顾小妹了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "我……我……我实在……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "我实在是看错你了，我本来还以为你是个男子汉大丈夫，谁知你却比……比豆腐还要软，你实在太令我伤心了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "阁下武功的确高明，但在下还是要来领教领教。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "留神，我要出手了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你是顾老四的什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "前……前辈莫非认得家父？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "听说顾老四的家教很严，怎容得你这样的子弟在江湖中招摇？要知越是会武功的人，越该要自己收敛，若是一言不合就胡乱出手，那就是盗贼匹夫所为，这道理你爹爹难道未曾教训过你么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？凭什么来教训我们？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们连他老人家是谁都不知道么？他就是大侠燕南天！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤以后永远再也不能欺世盗名，为非作歹了，你们也用不着再找他算账，因为已有别的人要先找他算账，那是二十年前的旧账。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是，是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "只望你们以后也莫要以武凌人，妄动杀手！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你龟儿子现在为什么不叫了？听说你们将燕南天在恶人谷中困了二十年，老子本来还不相信，现在看来，只怕真有这回事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "那是她和大嘴狼他们干的事，与我无关。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "既然与你无关，你龟儿子为什么怕成这副样子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你见了他难道不害怕么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "老子坏事做得没有你多，用不着像你龟儿子这么害怕。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "常言道，只有强奸的，没有逼赌的，可见逼人赌钱要比强奸更坏，我干的坏事最多也只不过是强奸而已，可是你……嘿嘿，你小子等着瞧吧，他若知道你就是恶赌鬼，不打扁你的脑袋才怪。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤这龟儿子怎会和燕南天走到一路的？这倒真是怪事。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我现在才想出江别鹤的来历了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "他有什么来历？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "他一定就是江琴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "江琴又是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "燕南天到恶人谷去，就是为了要找江琴复仇，因为江琴害了他的拜把兄弟江枫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "他既要找江琴复仇的，现在为何还不宰了他，反而带着他满街跑呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "因为他要先找到小鱼儿，叫小鱼儿亲手报仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "不错，想必就是这缘故，可是，他若找不到小鱼儿呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "他这辈子只怕是再也找不到那小坏蛋了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这龟儿岂非就是江别鹤的儿子江玉郎么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这父子两人究竟在搞什么鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "看来他必定是想来救他老子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "就凭这小杂种，只怕还没有这么大的本事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "他本事虽不大，花样却不少，连小鱼儿有时都会上他的当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "老子也知道他花样不少，但若要比小鱼儿，他还差得远。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你真的认得江小鱼？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "非但认得，而且还可以说是患难之交。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你……你最近见过他么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "前两天他还和晚辈在一起喝酒……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你可知道他现在到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "他的行踪一向很飘忽，但晚辈却也许能找得到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈就算有天大的胆子，也不敢在前辈面前说谎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，好，好……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "这小子来历不明，燕大侠你怎可轻信他说的话？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "闭嘴，在我面前，那有你说话之处？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 114,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    }
